import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import store from './store'
import axios from 'axios'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import router from './router'

import { Dialog, Table, FormItem ,Button, Form,Input} from 'element-ui'

Vue.use(VueRouter)
Vue.prototype.$axios = axios
Vue.config.producFormItemtionTip = false
Vue.use(Dialog)
Vue.use(Table )
Vue.use(FormItem )
Vue.use(Button )
Vue.use(Form)
Vue.use(Input)


new Vue({
  el:'#app',
  render: h => h(App),
  store,
  router
})
